dialogueBoxes.dialogue: This new job is stressful. Paperwork, accounting, transactions. logs... It seems as if they've dumped all the work on you, the new hire.
Maybe the employees were glad to have someone ranked lower than them to give the work to, or maybe you just didn't read your job description closely enough.
Either way, you need to plan how the hell you're gonna get all of these things done before they're due.
